Up for sale is a premium residential plot of 2400sqft located close to Magadi Road, Bangalore. With feasible dimensions 40 X 60 sqft, this residential plot approved under Bruhat Bengaluru Mahanagara Palike (BBMP) is perfect for constructing your dream house up to four floors along with a huge terrace. As this residential plot is facilitated with all the prime civic amenities like drainage facility, electricity poles along with street lights and provision for a water source, the prospective buyer can immediately start the construction work, if needed. You don't have to worry about security and safety, as this plot is situated in the heart of a prime residential neighbourhood with friendly neighbours. Be it schools, hospitals, shopping malls, banks, ATMs and other facilities, all are located within close proximity. <div class="m-srp-card__description js-content-read-more truncated">
Janaadhar Shubha is promoted by Janaadhar India Pvt. Ltd., a company dedicated to providing well designed, high quality homes at a budget. The company is part of the Jana group of companies and headed by Mr.Ramesh Ramanathan, a very well known social entrepreneur. Planned as a budget housing solution, Janaadhar Shubha is being developed on an 11.5 acres plot on the Attibele-Anekal Road, on the outskirts of Bangalore city. Located close to several of the city's major industrial belts, the township consists of 1128 apartments. An address to lifestyle BOLLINENI SILAS is a premium residential development within a 10 acres layout comprising of 650 plus Apartments. This gated community is located on Belathur Main road, Sadarmangala, Whitefield, Bangalore with fantastic connectivity to the surrounding MNC's, Education, Hospitals and Shopping Malls. Quality Construction: BSCPL Infrastructures is one of the largest infrastructure company in India carrying the finest civil engineering experience of 43 years. BSCPL Infrastructure is involved in a range of infra projects (Roads, Airport works, Bridges, Building construction, Irrigation and Railway freight corridor works), Real estate and Health care. The company has taken up Real Estate development projects in DUBAI, HYDERABAD, CHENNAI, and BENGALURU.

		/* if(result_count>20){
			_gaq.push([ '_trackEvent', 'NSR Result Count', 'Organic Count =' +result_count,'No NSR Result',0,true ]);
		} */
	

  	var sortByField = 'premiumRecent';
	if(sortByField && '0' == 0) {
	  	var label = '';
	  	var loginrfnum = '';
		if (typeof loginrfnum !== 'undefined' && loginrfnum != '') {
			label = 'Existing user';
		} else {
			label = 'New user';
		}
		if(sortByField.indexOf('premiumRecent') == -1 && '44996' > 0){
			if(sortByField && sortByField.indexOf('_New') != -1) {
				label = label + " | Managed for Good Properties | " + 44996;
			} else {
				label = label + " | Normal Sorting | " + 44996;
			}
		}
		ga('send', 'event', 'Sort', sortByField.replace("_New", ""), label);
	}
</script>

You also have Venkateshwara Layout bus stand within 500m for more convenient travelling through buses. Magadi Road is undeniably a beautiful locality to reside and is also a treat for property investors.               like.src = url;
              like.onload = function () {
                  if (typeof uex == 'function') { uex('ld', 'facebook_like_iframe', {wb: 1}); }
              };
           } else if (isAdvertisingThemed) {
              $('.social_networking_like').closest('.aux-content-widget-2').hide();
           }
        }

                }

        csv_writer.writerow(["Title","Duration","Description"])
        for card in cards:

            x = name.text

                y = duration.text
